metadata.name: October 3, 2019
metadata.description:
October 3, 2019: Florida man arrested for trying to get alligator drunk.

A Florida man was reportedly arrested for trying to get an alligator drunk after his pal captured the reptile.

Florida Man told authorities he had consumed a few beers that day, but claimed he wasnâ€™t intoxicated during the incident.

After the beer feeding, which was recorded, the duo released the animal back into the wild. 

Both men were arrested on Oct. 3 and charged with unlawfully taking an alligator.
